\subsection{[[Ctab]]}

%claude:
[[Ctab]] is the parallel table for \verb+ctl+ commands: each entry maps a
keyword (e.g. \verb+useragent+, \verb+headers+) to its type and to the
offset of the corresponding field inside [<Ctl>] or [<Client>]. Writes to
\verb+ctl+ become essentially data-driven assignments, with [<Xtype>] picking
the parser (bool, int, string, URL, function call).

