\subsection{[[Action]]}

%claude:
[[Action]] is the side-data hung off any [[Rtext]] that is more than plain
text. 

<<struct [[Action]](mothra)>>=
struct Action{

    // for <img src=... >
    char *image;
    // for <input ...>
