%claude:
The fields are tagged by which one is non-nil: an \verb+<a>+ anchor
sets \verb+link+; an \verb+<img>+ sets \verb+image+; an \verb+<input>+ sets
\verb+field+. 
%
\verb+ismap+ is the rare case where one item is both a link
and a server-side image map, so the click handler must add the
\verb+?x,y+ coordinate suffix. \verb+name+ is the anchor name that lets
\verb+#fragment+ scrolling work.


